unsw.dungeon

Class DungeonLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • unsw.dungeon.DungeonLoader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DungeonControllerLoader

    public abstract class DungeonLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Loads a dungeon from a .json file. By extending this class, a subclass can hook into entity creation. This is useful for creating UI elements with corresponding entities.
    Author:
    Robert Clifton-Everest
